latestPosts.caption:
Looking for a resort to enjoy monsoons from? I stayed at @cocoshambhala and it’s all sorts of luxury..! 

Villa Amaresha has a piece of my heart, I could sit by the pool and watch waves crashing the shores or rains dropping outside my window. 

Did I tell you, I tried cooking Malvani cuisine with the in-house chef because they organise cooking workshops apart from pottery and nature hikes. 

Can you believe it is just a 70-minute drive from #northgoa 

A place is all about the people who make you feel special- my travel partner @namratabs ensured we enjoy every bit of it, property manager Suhas who is always there to help guests, Chef Sherbahadur bringing the best of the food to our tables, and Redkar ji to show us around like a local. 

📍 Sindhudurg 
📸 @namratabs 
👗 @bougainvilleahyd

Think twice before choosing your adventure sport school..! 

Ensure if they’re authorised to run it, do they have expert instructors, do they follow safety measures, are equipment up to date, and most importantly- ARE THEY DISCPLINED AND SINCERE about it. I found all of them with @kadalsurfschool (not a sponsored post, a genuine review) 

Hands down 🙌🏻 @indiansurfergirl and @rohansuvarnaa are the best ones to learn Surfing and Stand up paddling from.. 

If you’re planning a trip to udupi, save this video and trust me on this recommendation.

Last travel of 2024 and living the best coastal life with @indiansurfergirl ♥️♥️♥️ 

📍 Udupi, Karnataka 

I met Tanvi (National surfing champion) online and the friendship grew so fond that we will be celebrating new years together, she’s showing me the best of Udupi, and teaching me how to surf- couldn’t have asked for a better way to end this fabulous year. 

After 5 days, I will give you an itinerary for Udupi till then enjoy this place from my lenses..!

Did you say Luxurious Staycation in Hyderabad?? 

Nothing beats the comfort and premium accommodation of @tridenthyderabad. You’ll feel like a King with the warm hospitality and Uber cool amenities they offer. Ranging from smart rooms to common spaces, food at on-site restaurants to IRD experience; everything is class apart. 

My absolute favourite is their (almost) 24*7 with live performances 🍻
